				<td colspan="2"><span>I get similar things.  I keep a twist of 4 songs up and people are asking me to join their guilds.  I think that there really are enough bards out there that play one random song, hit autoattack, and watch the pretty lights, that when someone does more, its amazing...  
<br />

<br />
Keep working on things... Don't get complacent.  And just keep those Ooh's and Ahh's coming... Think of the game as your stage, and your groups as your audience, as you keep them entertained with your Mad Skillz!!  =D
<br />

<br />
Keldridge</span></td>
