				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: what ARE people doing?<a name="45165"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 9 04 2:17 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Most people judge bards by the number of icons they keep up. However the best bards are usually the ones you don't even notice what they are doing, just that miraculously mobs die faster and the cleric has more mana. It's often the little things that make the big difference between bards, and in general only another bard would notice (and even then often they do not).
<br />

<br />
