Let me put it this way. Is the enchanter ONLY mezzing? Of course not. The casters are buffed with mana regen, the melee are hasted, at the same time that the enchanter is mezzing. If all your doing is mezzing, then your not providing NEAR the effectiveness of an enchanter.
